name: End You Up
description:
In "End You Up" your god asks you to kill yourself, but there are many protection layers on you, you'll need to be ingenious to understand how to do it.

"End You Up" is a 4-day long project made in ECV Lille - University (France) on GB Studio.

Control (keyboard):

  • Start game => Enter
  • Move => WASD/Arrow keys
  • Interact => E

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

/!\ Disclaimer/!\

I'm a French Student so I'm sorry if there is some syntax error in the game, do not hesitate to tell me so I can change them in a further update.

The game will probably receive updates in the future if I have time for it, It was a really nice experience and could be a great game if I put more effort into it. At first 50 different death were imagined but I had to reduce it because of the timing.

Made by Gemma "Solya" Lelli
